pageContext.claim: “The so-called leaks coming out of the White House are a massive over  exaggeration put out by the Fake News Media in order to make us look as bad as possible. With that being said, leakers are traitors and cowards, and we will find out who they are!”
pageContext.analysis: In this whiplash-inducing tweet, Trump refers to "so-called leaks" and then immediately afterward pledges to find out who the leakers are.
